responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "0519EB584FADD1EFA4272A97B21F4E1D", "A moot needed. Zinjala's actions, they threaten peace we build, cannot be ignored. Tribe must hear truth, choose our path. Zinjala want war, chaos, cling to old ways. I know him many seasons, fought beside him. We lock horns before, but he see my peace wish as weakness. He wrong. This crime must be faced; we cannot let rebellion destroy all we work for. Tribe must understand cost of his actions before we move forward.")
